  author   = "Lange, Joshua T and Chen, Celine Y and Pichugin, Yuriy and Xie,
              Frank and Tang, Jun and Hung, King L and Yost, Kathryn E and Shi,
              Quanming and Erb, Marcella L and Rajkumar, Utkrisht and Wu, Sihan
              and Swanton, Charles and Liu, Zhe and Huang, Weini and Chang,
